                    <span>Add a star if you are from Glen Cove or the local area. This book is not what I expected. I purchased thinking it would be an historical account of the mansion and its occupants but it turned out to a compelling ghost story. It was enjoyable and informative.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Interesting Account of the Gold Coast</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
