                    </div>
                    <span>This book is interesting in its account of the Woolworths and their haunted mansion. However, I was not impressed with the historical details in this book. This books seems more like a fictionalized account of a woman's experience in a haunted mansion than a non-fictional account. The fact that I learned very little of the life of the Woolworth and his life left me at a loss at the end of the book.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Ghost Story Memoir</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
